  "faqs": [
    {
      "question": "What is the Sona Comstar IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Sona Comstar IPO<!-- --> is a <b>main-board<!-- --> <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> of <!-- --> equity shares</b> of the face value of ₹<!-- -->10<!-- --> aggregating up to ₹<!-- -->5,550.00<!-- --> Crores. The issue is priced at <span>₹291 per share</span>. The minimum order quantity is <!-- -->51<!-- -->.</p><p>The <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> <b>opens on <!-- -->June 14, 2021</b>, and <b>closes on <!-- -->June 16, 2021</b>.</p><p>Kfin Technologies Limited<!-- --> is the registrar for the <!-- -->IPO<!-- -->. The shares are proposed to be listed on <!-- -->BSE, NSE<!-- -->.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "How to apply in Sona Comstar IPO through Zerodha?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Zerodha customers can apply online in <!-- -->Sona Comstar IPO<!-- --> using UPI as a payment gateway. Zerodha customers can apply in <!-- -->Sona Comstar IPO<!-- --> by login into Zerodha Console (back office) and submitting an IPO application form.</p><p><strong>Steps to apply in <!-- -->Sona Comstar IPO<!-- --> through Zerodha</strong></p><ol><li>Visit the Zerodha website and login to Console.</li><li>Go to Portfolio and click the IPOs link.</li><li>Go to the '<!-- -->Sona Comstar IPO<!-- -->' row and click the 'Bid' button.</li><li>Enter your UPI ID, Quantity, and Price.</li><li>Submit IPO application form.</li><li>Visit the UPI App (net banking or BHIM) to approve the mandate.</li></ol><p>Visit <a href=\"/broker/zerodha/ipo/18/\" title=\"Zerodha IPO Application Process Review\">Zerodha IPO Application Process Review</a> for more detail.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "When Sona Comstar IPO will open?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The Sona Comstar IPO opens on June 14, 2021 and closes on June 16, 2021.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "What is the lot size of Sona Comstar IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Sona Comstar IPO<!-- --> <b>lot size is <!-- -->51</b>, and the <b>minimum amount required is <span>₹14,841</span></b>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "How to apply for Sona Comstar IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>You can apply in <!-- -->Sona Comstar IPO<!-- --> online using either <a href=\"/article/upi-payment-option-ipo-application-explained/382/\">UPI</a> or ASBA as a payment method. ASBA IPO application is available in the net banking of your bank account. UPI IPO application is offered by brokers who don't offer banking services. Read more detail about applying IPO online through <a href=\"/broker/zerodha/ipo/18/\" title=\"Zerodha IPO Review\"><b>Zerodha</b></a>, <a href=\"/broker/upstox/ipo/33/\" title=\"Upstox IPO Review\">Upstox</a>, <a href=\"/broker/5paisa/ipo/4/\" title=\"5Paisa IPO Review\">5Paisa</a>, <a href=\"/broker/edelweiss_broking/ipo/34/\" title=\"Nuvama IPO Review\">Nuvama</a>, <a href=\"/broker/hdfc-securities/ipo/6/\" title=\"HDFC Bank IPO Review\">HDFC Bank</a>, and <a href=\"/broker/sbi-capital/ipo/19/\" title=\"SBI Capital IPO Review\">SBI Bank</a>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "When is Sona Comstar IPO allotment?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The finalization of Basis of Allotment for <!-- -->Sona Comstar IPO<!-- --> will be done on <!-- -->Monday, June 21, 2021<!-- -->, and the allotted shares will be credited to your demat account by <!-- -->Wednesday, June 23, 2021<!-- -->. Check the <a href=\"/ipo_allotment_status/sona-comstar-ipo/1112/\" title=\"Sona Comstar IPO Allotment Status\">Sona Comstar IPO<!-- --> allotment status</a>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
